            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"巴郡「後巴菲特時代」首封股東信：巴菲特仍坐鎮、現金3,733億美元不是退場訊號\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"710\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Rk0xnnbo2GRPwhiYVZtj.Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxMA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/3b975070-3542-11ee-bef5-35706f24738d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">巴郡「後巴菲特時代」首封股東信：巴菲特仍坐鎮、現金3,733億美元不是退場訊號</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%A2%E5%85%8B%E5%A4%8F-%E5%BE%8C%E5%B7%B4%E8%8F%B2%E7%89%B9%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3-%E9%A6%96%E5%B0%81%E8%82%A1%E6%9D%B1%E4%BF%A1-%E5%B7%B4%E8%8F%B2%E7%89%B9%E4%BB%8D%E5%9D%90%E9%8E%AE-%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%913-210003405.html",
